s/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />椰青水 洗鬼冷壓 一開椰青都有啦"},{"pid":"2305b9969cab2acaddbff7f945dea61a589aadca","tid":2105231,"uid":97582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ac4e3a4ee5130ddb6e1751f288b2c2e93226500","tid":2105231,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"見超市有D新鮮椰青<br />\n有埋飲管抆開個咀就飲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgzibGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgzibGh.jpg&h=a434df93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩見到就買咗黎試，都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950e355070cd406fb01098ed87115a9068a06542","tid":2105231,"uid":97582,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XqoVYnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXqoVYnB.jpg&h=565b1248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想同大家分享下開椰青神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打算買黎試下係咪真係咁方便"},{"pid":"e4aae70ec0c02697b6518ca85eb7612712d9849e","tid":2105231,"uid":76569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"見到標題 諗緊咖啡就話cold brew啫<br />\n椰青一開就有水 點冷壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcba66d5c7fd922153b0da8b5fe2c6bd72876da","tid":2105231,"uid":97582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4aae70ec0c02697b6518ca85eb7612712d9849e","tid":2105231,"uid":76569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"見到標題 諗緊咖啡就話cold brew啫<br />\n椰青一開就有水 點冷壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nk6c0BZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNk6c0BZ.png&h=25685e20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到台灣Family Mart出咗冷壓椰子水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle咗一下大概個技術：<br />\n<br />\n//HPP 保鮮技術是什麼？<br />\n<br />\nHPP 是 High Pressure Processing 的縮寫，是一種高壓殺菌技術，通常以 1,000 &ndash; 10,000 大氣壓的壓力來處理食物。在這樣的壓力下，能破壞微生物的細胞膜，進而發揮殺菌的作用。由於 HPP 是在低溫下進行的殺菌技術，因此不像傳統的加熱殺菌會經過高溫處理，使用 HPP 理論上相對能維持食物原來的風味。<br />\n<br />\n基於高壓與相對較低的溫度加工，或許就是這款椰子水上說它自己是「冷壓」的理由吧！但是全家使用 HPP 這個技術所宣稱的「冷壓」，和橄欖油、苦茶油或是其他油品的冷壓應該是不一樣的喔。//"},{"pid":"c6ff66d235126abf10717c12c4e33143ef7d7dee","tid":2105231,"uid":247737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"bless？"},{"pid":"f3ac9f65f417520f739d72c2fa021843c8adc364","tid":2105231,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2305b9969cab2acaddbff7f945dea61a589aadca","tid":2105231,"uid":97582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ac4e3a4ee5130ddb6e1751f288b2c2e93226500","tid":2105231,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"見超市有D新鮮椰青<br />\n有埋飲管抆開個咀就飲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgzibGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgzibGh.jpg&h=a434df93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩見到就買咗黎試，都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"不過無得劈開佢食埋椰肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}